org.glassfish.sse.api

Class ServerSentEventData

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.glassfish.sse.api.ServerSentEventData

  • public final class ServerSentEventData
extends Object
    Represents a Server-Sent Event data.

    new ServerSentEventData().data("YHOO").data("+2").data("10) would send the following event (followed by blank line): 

     data:YHOO
 data:+2
 data:10

    new ServerSentEventData().comment("test stream") would send the following event (followed by blank line): 

     :test stream

    new ServerSentEventData().data("first event").id("1") would send the following event (followed by blank line): 

     data:first event
 id:1

    new ServerSentEventData().event("add").data("73857293") would send the following event (followed by blank line): 

     event:add
 data:73857293
    Author:
    Jitendra Kotamraju
